Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:22.57,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Polly Jean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:25.53,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We'll never be away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:27.12,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We're going
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:31.62,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We're always here in between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:40.05,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}The shadows and the trees, in between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:44.05,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Like sunshine trickling through the leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:48.01,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I want to feel something real
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:51.60,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Like rivers overflowing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:55.81,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I want to be set free
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:59.48,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Now everything is part of me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:03.61,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}A world to reach, nothing to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:07.16,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I don't know where they're going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:11.16,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Now won't you come find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:15.12,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Though I try, and I try, and I try, and I try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:18.67,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Can never shake off this feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:22.96,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Don't know why, don't know why, don't know why, don't know why
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:26.72,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Why we hide from you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:28.14,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Polly Jean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:31.89,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We'll never be away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:33.39,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We're going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:38.02,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}We're always here in between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:41.65,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Those shadows everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:43.28,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Seventeen
